This refined tie is handcrafted in Italy from luxurious silk and features a classic polka-dot pattern.
  • Handmade with a fully fitted interlining that ensures a beautiful drape and a smooth, even knot.
  • Tip is lined with pure silk twill, which is a hallmark of superior necktie construction.
  • 3¼" wide. 100% silk. Dry clean. Made in Italy.

name: Turnbull & Asser Ribbed Silk Tie
desc:
Each Turnbull & Asser silk tie is individually handmade in London, England to ensure high quality and an impeccable finish. Its ribbed appearance will add subtle flair to your most formal looks. Shown here with a Charvet shirt . The slimmer width of this tie is exclusively for MR PORTER.
  • Black ribbed silk satin tie
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Handmade in London, England

name: Charvet Knitted Silk Tie
desc:
Heritage Parisian company Charvet is globally renowned for its high quality materials and expert construction, aptly demonstrated by this impeccable knitted silk tie. This piece is flawlessly constructed in Italy in a slim profile that works best with streamlined silhouettes. Gift it to the gentleman who appreciates luxurious details with panache. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Yellow knitted-silk tie
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy

name: Lanvin Knitted Silk Bow Tie
desc:
Crafted in France from pure silk in a black shade, this Lanvin bow tie is assured and elegant. The subtle contrast of textures with the knitted front and woven back add the subtlest detail to evening outfits and demonstrate a command of black tie style.
  • Black layered knitted silk and plain-woven bow tie
  • Pre-tied style, adjustable neck strap
  • Hook and eye fastening
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in France

name: Drake's Polka-Dot Silk Tie
desc:
This splendid Drake's tie has been hand sewn, dyed and assembled in London. The navy and white polka pattern is sure to be a modern classic, contrast it against a check or striped shirt for the most stylish take. Shown here with a Charvet tie .
  • Navy silk tie
  • White polka-dot print
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Handmade in London, England

name: Lanvin Knitted Silk Tie
desc:
Inject smart outfits with a splash of opulent colour with Lanvin 's grape tie. Knitted in Italy from lustrous silk, it makes a dapper impression worn against any shade. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Grape knitted silk tie
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy

name: Brioni Knitted Silk Tie
desc:
Knitted ties are a classic addition to any wardrobe and this hand-finished version from Brioni will bring an air of finesse to any outfit. The easy-to-wear light blue hue goes superbly with crisp whites and soft pinks - team it with these colour palettes for an accomplished look. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Light blue knitted-silk tie
  • Small 'b' logo
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Handmade in Italy

name: Brooks Brothers Silk Double Bow Tie
desc:
Having dressed the likes of Presidents John F. Kennedy and Abraham Lincoln, American label Brooks Brothers is a fail-safe choice for formal occasions. For an evening formula that will guarantee sartorial success, team this impeccable silk double bow tie with a bib-front shirt and a tuxedo.
  • Black silk double bow tie
  • Adjustable strap, pre-tied style
  • Hook and eye fastening
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in the USA

name: Turnbull & Asser Silk Bow Tie
desc:
When choosing a bow tie for a black tie outfit, a foolproof tip is to match your tie to the lapel of your jacket. In the case of this self-tie Turnbull & Asser design, opt for a silk lapel with a slight sheen. A dress shirt, blazer and Cary Grant swagger will take you through the evening in impeccable style.
  • Black silk bow tie
  • Self-tie style, adjustable red grosgrain strap
  • Clip fastening
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in England

name: Alfred Dunhill Patterned Mulberry Silk Tie
desc:
Meticulously made in England from fine mulberry silk, Alfred Dunhill 's sleek silk tie typifies the British company's dedication to superlative craftsmanship. This dapper piece comes in an understated two-tone pattern complete with neatly stitched stripes adding a dash of flair to your sharp city line-up. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Navy and burgundy woven mulberry silk tie
  • Silver stitched stripe pattern
  • 100% mulberry silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in England

name: Lanvin Polka-Dot Silk-Faille Tie
desc:
Pristinely crafted in France, Lanvin 's silk-faille tie is a timeless accessory to stock in your desk-to-dinner repertoire. Designed in a deep midnight-blue hue and woven with white polka dots, it looks just as polished in the boardroom as it does on a date. Let yours stand out against a crisp white shirt. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Midnight blue silk-faille tie
  • White woven polka dots
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in France

name: Drake's Printed Silk Tie
desc:
This handsome Drake's tie has been hand printed in England using traditional dye and discharge methods, resulting in crisp, bright colours. The blue and white patterning will look best against a classic white shirt and navy or grey tailoring. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Blue silk tie
  • White circle print
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in England

name: Charvet Knitted Silk Tie
desc:
Favoured by redoubtable style icons from Mr. Frank Sinatra to Mr. Sean Connery, the knitted tie is a style that keeps the best company and Charvet 's navy silk design is among the most refined we've seen. Team this subtly textured piece with a sharply cut mohair suit for a self-assured evening look.Shown here with a Charvet shirt . Designed exclusively for MR PORTER
  • Navy knitted silk tie
  • Squared end
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy

name: Etro Paisley-Print Silk Tie
desc:
Italian luxury brand Etro is known for its artful and sophisticated use of colour. Work the brand's signature paisley motif into formal looks with this silk tie. Designed in rich hues of navy, indigo, lavender and turquoise, we think it looks best against dark suiting. Wear it against a crisp white shirt to fully showcase the elegant piece. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Multi-coloured paisley-print silk tie
  • 100% silk; lining: 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy

name: Lanvin Knitted Silk Tie
desc:

  • Forest green knitted silk tie

  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy

desc:

desc:

  • Dry clean

name: Hackett Silk Bow Tie
desc:

This black silk bow tie is an incredibly smart option for your tuxedo. Designed to be tied yourself, you can either wear it squared-up and crisp or a little off-centre for a more rakish take. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .

  • Dry clean

name: Charvet Knitted Silk Tie
desc:
Founded in 1838 in Paris, Charvet still stands for exceptional refinement to this day. Immaculately crafted in Italy from high quality silk, this narrow-cut knitted tie embodies the ethos. Wear this lively green piece to lend a sharp collared shirt a double dose of luxury and panache. Shown here with a Charvet shirt . Designed exclusively for MR PORTER
  • Green knitted-silk tie
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy

name: Charvet Slim Knitted Silk Tie
desc:
The combination of lustrous silk and rugged texture makes Charvet 's knitted tie a raffish and versatile way to define your look. Wear it with a herringbone blazer and a crisp white shirt to channel the dapper vintage aesthetic of Mr. Jarvis Cocker. Shown here with a Charvet shirt . Designed exclusively for MR PORTER
  • Brown knitted silk tie
  • Squared end
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy
